Package lab5.supermarketsimulation.events

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    SupermarketArrivalEvent
    This Event represent a customer arriving to the store.
    SupermarketClosingEvent
    This Event represent the store closing.
    SupermarketEvent
    This Event represent the general supermarket event.
    SupermarketGatherEvent
    This Event represent when a customer has gathered their supplies and are ready to pay
    SupermarketPayEvent
    The event that is executed when a customer has payed for their supplies
    SupermarketStartEvent
    This event starts the supermarket simulation by adding the first customer
    SupermarketStopEvent
    This event stop the supermarket simulation
